# WhatsApp Bot Responsive Design Rules

## Genel Responsive Kuralları

### 1. Container Yapısı

- Container'ları çok iç içe yapma
- Her section için ayrı container kullan
- Mobile-first yaklaşım uygula
- Grid sistemini responsive yap

### 2. Breakpoint Sistemi

- `sm:` (640px+) - Small devices
- `md:` (768px+) - Medium devices
- `lg:` (1024px+) - Large devices
- `xl:` (1280px+) - Extra large devices

### 3. Spacing Sistemi

- Mobile: `p-4`, `gap-4`, `space-y-4`
- Desktop: `md:p-6`, `md:gap-6`, `md:space-y-6`
- Large: `lg:p-8`, `lg:gap-8`, `lg:space-y-8`

### 4. Typography Responsive

- Mobile: `text-sm`, `text-lg`, `text-2xl`
- Desktop: `md:text-base`, `md:text-xl`, `md:text-4xl`

### 5. Icon Sizing

- Mobile: `w-8 h-8`, `text-lg`
- Desktop: `md:w-10 md:h-10`, `md:text-xl`

